data.description: Completely Remodeled and Spacious 2 Bedroom 1 Bath with 2 Parking spaces Assigned to this unit. Low HOA of $270. Get some fresh air and enjoy Huge Balcony with access sliding doors between the living room and primary bedroom. In the heart of Hialeah, very well maintained building with Security Patrol.  Walking distance from shopping malls, easy access to palmetto expressway.
